# FindX11_XCB
# -----------
#
# This will define the following variables:
#
# ``X11_XCB_FOUND``
#     System has libX11-xcb
# ``X11_XCB_LIBRARIES``
#     Link these to use libX11-xcb
# ``X11_XCB_INCLUDE_DIR``
#     The libX11-xcb include dir
# ``X11_XCB_DEFINITIONS``
#     Compiler switches required for using libX11-xcb

